org.javimmutable.collections

Interface Indexed<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    JImmutableArray<T>, JImmutableList<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndexedArray, IndexedList, JImmutableTreeList, JImmutableTrieArray, Subindexed

    public interface Indexed<T>
    Interface for containers that allow access to values by an integer index.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • get

        T get(int index)
        Retrieve the value. The index must be valid for the container's current size (i.e. [0-size)
        Throws:
